          <li>Identify how trust can be misused in everyday situations.</li>
          <li>Build awareness of safe help-seeking behavior.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="ap-panel">
        <h2>Learning Outcomes</h2>
        <ul class="ap-list">
          <li>Recognize common tactics used to gain a child’s trust.</li>
          <li>Explain why personal boundaries and privacy matter.</li>
          <li>Practice safer decision-making with trusted adults.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="ap-section">
      <div class="ap-section__header">
        <h2>Module Content</h2>
        <p class="ap-section__subtitle">Download materials for each submodule and preview what is included.</p>
      </div>

